"如果您希望操作系统优先处理键盘快捷键，并将未使用的快捷键发送给 Ansel，请选中"
"此项。否则，只要 Ansel 处于活动状态，它就会捕获所有按键，这可能会导致某些操作"
"系统上的系统级快捷键完全失效。"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4729
msgid "sort built-in presets first"
msgstr "先对内置预设排序"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4743
msgid ""
"whether to show built-in presets first before user's presets in presets menu."
msgstr "是否先显示内置预设，然后在预设菜单中显示用户预设。"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4765
msgid "Disable thumbnail preview in import popup"
msgstr "禁用导入弹出窗口中的缩略图预览"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4779
msgid ""
"Check this if you are impacted by extra-slow loading when accessing images "
"on memory card through camera USB link and PTP/MTP drivers."
msgstr ""
"如果您在使用相机 USB 连接和 PTP/MTP 驱动程序访问存储卡上的图像时遇到加载速度"
"异常慢的问题，请检查此项。"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4801
msgid "method to use for getting the display profile"
msgstr "用于获取显示配置文件的方法"

#: ../build/src/preferences_gen.h:4844
msgid ""
"this option allows to force a specific means of getting the current display "
"profile. this is useful when one alternative gives wrong results"
msgstr ""
"此选项可以指定使用特定方式获取显示器的色彩管理配置。当其中一个方式返回错误结"
"果时请使用此选项。"

#. tags
