msgid "Imported:"
msgstr "已导入："

#: ../src/common/import.c:1156
msgid ""
"Images already in the library will not be imported again, selected or not. "
"Remove them from the library first, or use the menu `Run → Resynchronize "
"library and XMP` to update the local database from distant XMP.\n"
"\n"
"Ansel indexes images by their filename and parent folder (full path), not by "
"their content. Therefore, renaming or moving images on the filesystem, or "
"changing the mounting point of their external drive will make them look like "
"new (unknown) images.\n"
"\n"
"If an XMP file is present alongside images, it will be imported as well, "
"including the metadata and settings stored in it. If it is not what you "
"want, you can reset metadata in the lighttable."
msgstr ""
"已经位于照片库中的图片将不会被再次导入，无论是否被选中。如果想通过 XMP 文件更"
"新本地数据库，需要先从照片库中移除图片，或者使用“运行”菜单中的“重新同步 XMP "
"文件与照片库”。\n"
"\n"
"Ansel 使用文件名和所在目录（完整路径）来索引图片而不是使用文件内容。因此，重"
"命名或者在文件系统上移动文件，或者改变了外置磁盘的挂载点将会使文件看起来像新"
"（未知）图片。\n"
"\n"
"如果存在和图片对应的 XMP 文件，那么它将会被一起导入，这包括存储在里面的元数据"
"和设置。如果您不想这样，可以在光台中重置元数据。"

