"adjust the color and shade of the film transparent base.\n"
"this value depends on the film material, \n"
"the chemical fog produced while developing the film,\n"
"and the scanner white balance."
msgstr ""
"调整胶片透明底座的颜色和色度。\n"
"这个值取决于胶片材料，\n"
"冲洗胶片时产生的化学雾，\n"
